snippet.title: Jelly Escape Release Trailer
snippet.description:
This is the release trailer for the upcoming funny tricky platformer retro 80's arcade TawStudio's new title: Jelly Escape!

Can you manage to escape over 60 chambers of imprisoning laboratories, while unlocking several other jellies, chambers, and bonus contents?

You can play the game for free right now! Here: (Coming Soon)

Stay tuned for news and updates through our channels:
Twitter: @TawStudio
Facebook: /TawStudio

And through ArmorGames channels:
Twitter: @ArmorGames
Facebook: /ArmorGames
